1
00:00:32,320 --> 00:00:34,784
You think I’m going down alone?

2
00:00:34,808 --> 00:00:35,920
Mom, please... stop.

3
00:00:37,580 --> 00:00:41,032
Now, that sister you love so much

4
00:00:41,420 --> 00:00:44,800
is going to be condemned by society as a pervert.

5
00:00:45,150 --> 00:00:47,296
accused of sexual abuse, incest.

6
00:00:47,352 --> 00:00:49,624
Mom, that’s enough!

7
00:00:51,210 --> 00:00:51,784
Why?

8
00:00:52,830 --> 00:00:54,080
Can't handle the truth?

9
00:00:55,020 --> 00:00:56,928
Well, I can't handle it either!

10
00:00:57,360 --> 00:00:59,872
Right now, I hate you so much.

11
00:00:59,912 --> 00:01:01,600
I can’t even stand the sight of your face!

12
00:01:04,350 --> 00:01:05,120
Mom...

13
00:01:12,930 --> 00:01:14,352
I’m begging you.

14
00:01:15,024 --> 00:01:17,020
If you give up now, it’s not too late.

15
00:01:19,300 --> 00:01:21,560
I’ve come too far to turn back now,

16
00:01:22,520 --> 00:01:23,480
you ungrateful brat!

17
00:01:24,240 --> 00:01:24,880
Mom.

18
00:01:25,704 --> 00:01:29,464
Just you wait... and watch Pimchat’s life crumble to pieces.

19
00:01:59,250 --> 00:02:00,808
What are we going to do now?

20
00:02:00,848 --> 00:02:02,810
This has blown up way out of proportion.

21
00:02:02,848 --> 00:02:04,136
Even the stock prices are crashing.

22
00:02:07,100 --> 00:02:08,672
I have my own way of handling this.

23
00:02:11,340 --> 00:02:14,760
You need to just tell the truth already.

24
00:02:14,816 --> 00:02:17,376
Now that your reputation is being destroyed,

25
00:02:17,800 --> 00:02:19,312
are you really going to stay silent?

26
00:02:21,020 --> 00:02:22,664
But if I speak up,

27
00:02:22,696 --> 00:02:24,660
you’re going to get dragged into this too.

28
00:02:25,510 --> 00:02:27,072
I don’t care, P’Chat.

29
00:02:27,500 --> 00:02:28,816
My mom doesn’t care either.

30
00:02:31,370 --> 00:02:32,320
I’ve made my choice.

31
00:02:33,930 --> 00:02:35,512
Ran! Ran!

32
00:02:35,576 --> 00:02:37,504
Ran! Ran! Wait...

33
00:02:38,860 --> 00:02:40,112
Where are you going?

34
00:02:41,820 --> 00:02:43,480
Stop trying to protect me.

35
00:02:45,260 --> 00:02:45,808
Ran.

36
00:02:46,670 --> 00:02:49,400
If you don't say it, I'll say it myself.

37
00:02:55,940 --> 00:02:58,176
Okay, okay. We’ll talk about this.

38
00:03:02,180 --> 00:03:04,192
I’ll be the one to speak.

39
00:03:05,500 --> 00:03:06,648
No, P’Chat.

40
00:03:08,250 --> 00:03:10,008
I’m going to end this myself.

41
00:03:16,770 --> 00:03:18,600
I'll be right there by your side.

42
00:03:29,008 --> 00:03:30,256
Alright, everyone.

43
00:03:30,860 --> 00:03:34,352
Today’s agenda, I am calling for a vote

44
00:03:34,810 --> 00:03:36,304
to remove Khun Pimchat

45
00:03:36,352 --> 00:03:39,064
from her position as Executive Vice President.

46
00:03:39,580 --> 00:03:40,744
Does everyone agree?

47
00:03:42,740 --> 00:03:43,728
Wait a moment.

48
00:03:45,512 --> 00:03:47,510
I have something to say first.

49
00:03:49,900 --> 00:03:54,208
I’d like to invite someone directly involved in this matter to come in.

50
00:04:20,240 --> 00:04:23,968
I am involved in this as well.

51
00:04:31,460 --> 00:04:33,288
and I would like to explain that...

52
00:04:39,110 --> 00:04:43,680
Everything that happened was not a scandal.

53
00:04:53,136 --> 00:04:55,140
Ran, stop it.

54
00:04:55,980 --> 00:04:58,816
No matter how much Pimchat has brainwashed you,

55
00:04:59,170 --> 00:05:02,616
you need to have some sense of right and wrong yourself.

56
00:05:05,130 --> 00:05:06,624
It’s because I do know, Mom,

57
00:05:07,380 --> 00:05:08,488
that I have to speak up.

58
00:05:23,512 --> 00:05:27,120
I, Ms. Ranya,

59
00:05:32,690 --> 00:05:35,632
am not a blood relative of Khun Pimchat.

60
00:05:43,776 --> 00:05:46,920
You... What the hell are you talking about?!

61
00:06:12,380 --> 00:06:13,824
These are the DNA test results.

62
00:06:17,030 --> 00:06:20,000
Khun Pimchat and I went to get tested.

63
00:06:21,110 --> 00:06:23,960
and it turns out it doesn't match.

64
00:06:29,170 --> 00:06:31,984
Wait... so that means..

65
00:06:32,460 --> 00:06:33,328
Yes.

66
00:06:34,740 --> 00:06:39,336
Khun Jintana lied to Khun Wichai, claiming I was his daughter

67
00:06:40,340 --> 00:06:41,704
just to exploit him for her own gain.

68
00:06:46,810 --> 00:06:48,216
Shut your mouth right now!

69
00:06:48,272 --> 00:06:49,256
How dare you say that?!

70
00:06:49,420 --> 00:06:52,360
Mom Mom, please stop.

71
00:06:52,408 --> 00:06:57,504
You... have the two of you been plotting against me this whole time? 	

72
00:06:58,800 --> 00:07:02,224
Everyone, this is a setup to frame me!

73
00:07:02,256 --> 00:07:03,592
It’s not true!

74
00:07:04,350 --> 00:07:05,576
It’s all a plot!

75
00:07:06,830 --> 00:07:09,712
My relationship with Ranya is real.

76
00:07:14,310 --> 00:07:17,336
But we only moved forward after we discovered we weren't actually sisters. 	Therefore,

77
00:07:21,630 --> 00:07:27,400
I—Pimchat Akkarapaisansakul

78
00:07:27,860 --> 00:07:31,392
am the sole heir to PS Group.

79
00:07:40,620 --> 00:07:43,280
Mom, please, just stop.

80
00:07:44,810 --> 00:07:45,888
Ungrateful child!

81
00:07:46,820 --> 00:07:48,104
You should have just died!

82
00:07:49,220 --> 00:07:50,968
If it weren't for you,

83
00:07:51,008 --> 00:07:52,424
my life would be perfect by now!

84
00:07:52,472 --> 00:07:53,760
You ungrateful brat!

85
00:07:55,130 --> 00:07:55,784
Mom... Mom!
